The evidence with the title 'Daphne Zuniga - Wikipedia ' says Daphne Eurydice Zuniga is an American actress. She made her film debut in 1982 in the slasher film The Dorm That Dripped Blood at the age of 19, followed by a lead role in the horror film The Initiation (1984) two years later.  ... After leaving college, Zuniga was close friends and roommates with fellow actress Meg Ryan. 
